{
  "stem": "9730.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think this may already have been after I moved out of the area, so that it would have perhaps been a few weeks after liberation.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I just happened to come that evening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when the doctors in fact had given up hope, I came.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And apparently that got her to-- gave her some sort of a boost in her morale, and-- and she pulled through.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were, of course, to-- to interrogate-- first of all, to round up any known high-level Nazis or possibly-- and/or war criminals and to-- to find them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we kept a-- a stockade in that intelligence center, where-- where we had found already a number of collaborationists from other countries who had collaborated with the Germans, some of them pretty high level, and some of the-- some of their war criminals, some-- some others who had been with the-- with special German commando units that-- I remember one of them, his name was Skorzeny.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had engineered the kidnapping of Mussolini-- I think it may have been away from partisans at the time-- and who had-- who had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] done some of those major feats that were accomplished during that time.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he himself had been imprisoned several times, each time escaping, and in fact escaped from-- from our enclosure as well, never to be heard from again, to my knowledge.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the name today doesn't mean too much, but there was a Yugoslav collaborationist by name of Tiso.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a high-level government official who was found-- found to be guilty of war crimes and was later hanged.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came back in October.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of '45.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
